---
const { image } = Astro.props;
---
<section class="mx-8">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4">
    <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-6">
      <img src={image} alt="Contact" class="w-full h-auto object-cover"/>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 lg:col-start-8 flex flex-col justify-end text-xl lg:text-2xl">
      <p class="indent-14 leading-normal text-boulder-900 text-xl lg:text-2xl"> 
        I’m a full-stack developer based in Valencia, always eager to tackle new challenges and bring ideas to life. Whether you have a clear plan or just the spark of an idea, I’d love to collaborate with you. Open to working with clients and teams worldwide—let’s build something great together.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:me@piergorelli.com" class="font-bold mt-8 text-2xl lg:text-3xl underline">me@piergorelli.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>